{"tid":1259762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"梁頌恆個3個人去咗邊？","createTime":"2019-06-26T16:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T16:49:21.000Z","uid":58430,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a985a2e227e89e723db0e7fb2ddf4fc5c0f7fbb5","tid":1259762,"uid":58430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:14:49.000Z","msg":"唔係話分化 而且雖則話兄弟爬山<br />\n但係咪兄弟有可能瀨野都唔出聲呀？<br />\n<br />\n而家圍狗總唔明個意義係邊？<br />\n又唔係阻返工阻食飯阻放工<br />\n一陣比哂位人入<br />\n而且夜媽媽啲狗冇性 <br />\n唔想再有義士受傷<br />\n個度地埋位置又唔好 <br />\n啲狗一封後面就好難走<br />\n<br />\n好啦 唔圍唔圍都成千人去咗<br />\n算了 不割蓆 一齊去一齊散<br />\n但Be water<br />\n而家都12點係咪應該散先 <br />\n聽日再留力圍律政<br />\n<br />\n最重點想問 吹雞圍狗屋個3個<br />\n梁頌恆 楊逸朗 鍾翰林<br />\n而家到底係邊？仲係唔係前線？"},{"pid":"1de379db1ca637cafecffddc39261e52c883de1d","tid":1259762,"uid":31324,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"應該唔會又搭的士掛"},{"pid":"4409f40a3d30d0374913fce5afccada73a24b777","tid":1259762,"uid":85803,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"有名你叫的士梁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe142a3c3a2d51e8059cc93b1dc2a376d0e4b3a","tid":1259762,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"尋人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3663947e9b5e44fc70e52f4b0b6ad29eb30249a","tid":1259762,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7171ee42f8c6e6d9fc1dba3fcfdaf7b50c48bc7b","tid":1259762,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔離個post係咁屌， 不過接受現實啦"}]}